---
interface Props {
  bgColor?: string;
}

const { bgColor = 'bg-slate-100' } = Astro.props;
---

<section class={`px-6 py-16 md:py-24 ${bgColor}`}>
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
    <!-- Section Header -->
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">
        Roof Questions? We Answer Them.
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-slate-600">
        These are the questions we hear every week from Northern Utah homeowners.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- FAQ Items -->
    <div class="space-y-6">
      <!-- FAQ Item 1 -->
      <details class="group bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-lg p-6 cursor-pointer hover:shadow-md transition shadow-md">
        <summary class="flex items-center justify-between font-semibold text-slate-900 text-lg">
          <span>Is the roof inspection really free?</span>
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-[#76ba41] group-open:rotate-180 transition" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 14l-7 7m0 0l-7-7m7 7V3" />
          </svg>
        </summary>
        <p class="text-slate-600 mt-4 leading-relaxed">
          Yes, completely free. We don't charge for assessments, and there's no obligation to move forward.
        </p>
      </details>

      <!-- FAQ Item 2 -->
      <details class="group bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-lg p-6 cursor-pointer hover:shadow-md transition shadow-md">
        <summary class="flex items-center justify-between font-semibold text-slate-900 text-lg">
          <span>How long does an assessment take?</span>
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-[#76ba41] group-open:rotate-180 transition" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 14l-7 7m0 0l-7-7m7 7V3" />
          </svg>
        </summary>
        <p class="text-slate-600 mt-4 leading-relaxed">
          Usually 30–45 minutes. We walk the roof, check the attic, take photos, and explain what we find.
        </p>
      </details>

      <!-- FAQ Item 3 -->
      <details class="group bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-lg p-6 cursor-pointer hover:shadow-md transition shadow-md">
        <summary class="flex items-center justify-between font-semibold text-slate-900 text-lg">
          <span>Do I need to be home for the inspection?</span>
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-[#76ba41] group-open:rotate-180 transition" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 14l-7 7m0 0l-7-7m7 7V3" />
          </svg>
        </summary>
        <p class="text-slate-600 mt-4 leading-relaxed">
          Yes, we need access to the attic and want to show you what we find in person.
        </p>
      </details>

      <!-- FAQ Item 4 -->
      <details class="group bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-lg p-6 cursor-pointer hover:shadow-md transition shadow-md">
        <summary class="flex items-center justify-between font-semibold text-slate-900 text-lg">
          <span>What if I can't afford a new roof right now?</span>
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-[#76ba41] group-open:rotate-180 transition" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 14l-7 7m0 0l-7-7m7 7V3" />
          </svg>
        </summary>
        <p class="text-slate-600 mt-4 leading-relaxed">
          We'll tell you the honest timeline. Sometimes repairs buy you time. Sometimes financing makes sense. We help you figure it out.
        </p>
      </details>

      <!-- FAQ Item 5 -->
      <details class="group bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-lg p-6 cursor-pointer hover:shadow-md transition shadow-md">
        <summary class="flex items-center justify-between font-semibold text-slate-900 text-lg">
          <span>Will you pressure me into a sale?</span>
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-[#76ba41] group-open:rotate-180 transition" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 14l-7 7m0 0l-7-7m7 7V3" />
          </svg>
        </summary>
        <p class="text-slate-600 mt-4 leading-relaxed">
          No. We educate you on your options and let you decide. That's it.
        </p>
      </details>

      <!-- FAQ Item 6 -->
      <details class="group bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-lg p-6 cursor-pointer hover:shadow-md transition shadow-md">
        <summary class="flex items-center justify-between font-semibold text-slate-900 text-lg">
          <span>How long does a roof replacement take?</span>
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-[#76ba41] group-open:rotate-180 transition" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 14l-7 7m0 0l-7-7m7 7V3" />
          </svg>
        </summary>
        <p class="text-slate-600 mt-4 leading-relaxed">
          Usually 2–5 days depending on size and complexity. We'll give you exact timeline before we start.
        </p>
      </details>

      <!-- FAQ Item 7 -->
      <details class="group bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-lg p-6 cursor-pointer hover:shadow-md transition shadow-md">
        <summary class="flex items-center justify-between font-semibold text-slate-900 text-lg">
          <span>What if insurance should cover this?</span>
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-[#76ba41] group-open:rotate-180 transition" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 14l-7 7m0 0l-7-7m7 7V3" />
          </svg>
        </summary>
        <p class="text-slate-600 mt-4 leading-relaxed">
          We help navigate insurance claims. We'll work with your adjuster and handle the process.
        </p>
      </details>

      <!-- FAQ Item 8 -->
      <details class="group bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-lg p-6 cursor-pointer hover:shadow-md transition shadow-md">
        <summary class="flex items-center justify-between font-semibold text-slate-900 text-lg">
          <span>What warranty do you offer?</span>
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-[#76ba41] group-open:rotate-180 transition" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 14l-7 7m0 0l-7-7m7 7V3" />
          </svg>
        </summary>
        <p class="text-slate-600 mt-4 leading-relaxed">
          5-year workmanship warranty on all installations. Plus manufacturer warranties on materials.
        </p>
      </details>
    </div>

    <!-- Still Have Questions CTA -->
    <div class="mt-12 text-center">
      <a 
        href="#form"
        class="inline-block rounded-lg bg-[#76ba41] text-white px-8 py-4 text-lg font-semibold hover:bg-[#5fa033] transition duration-200"
      >
        Still have questions? Let’s talk.
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>